{"tid":178034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺689開始發癲亂咬，肯定佢依家好憎香港人","createTime":"2017-03-29T09:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T10:38:18.000Z","uid":14503,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b1ef129ed381858993951f8c9bbd369262ea6c1","tid":178034,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"係佢在任期間我地又講佢個女講佢老婆呢樣個樣又話查佢UGL，佢一定好憎香港人。<br />\n<br />\n佢依家就黎唔做十足十遞左信就發脾氣個d人咁，咩氣都係呢個時候發，依家先黎搞TSA又告呢個告果個。<br />\n<br />\n本身想抽後算帳佢，點知佢依家仲要有個金鐘罩全國政協副主席做，UGL免疫，依家仲掉返轉比佢清算返轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n呢條友真係壞事做盡完全冇撚誠信，卑鄙無恥下9流賤9格，依家仲比佢高高在上遮住半邊咀笑真係好唔忿氣，相對貪曾真係陰9功。<br />\n<br />\n記得當年佢話: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「日後我會一如既往，繼續帶住一張凳，一本簿，一支筆，同我的管治團隊，走入群眾，聽取你地的意見。我，梁振英，希望做一個親民的特首，今日我作出的所有承諾，將會成為歷史紀錄，我會在陽光下，接受全港700萬市民監督。」</span></strong> 真係屌佢它罪母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係愈諗愈嬲，點解呢個衰人冇惡報仲可以咁囂張得威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢卸任之後9成9都會繼續玩9香港人，點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef12a8deaa34fdf420267238e427a777c90e5072","tid":178034,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27df906a1eecb4e45ac180ff445d8edb522a491b","tid":178034,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6e33f020552d804d81f1a94bca05ef5661d9cd","tid":178034,"uid":65892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T11:31:29.000Z","m